Package: plotteR
Type: Package
Title: An R Package with Utilities for Graphics and Plots 
Version: 0.8.7
Author: Dr. Thomas Weise <tweise@hfuu.edu.cn>
Maintainer: Dr. Thomas Weise <tweise@hfuu.edu.cn>
Description: In this package, we put some simple utilities for graphics and plots. The main goal is to provide some wrapper around the `plot` function to make it easier to plot several data sets coming from a list (\code{\link{batchPlot.list}}) or a list of objects/lists (\code{\link{batchPlot.groups}}). These plots then can automatically use distinctive colors.
License: LGPL-3
Encoding: UTF-8
URL: http://www.github.com/thomasWeise/plotteR
